snippet.title: Polyamory increases in popularity as record numbers flock to dating apps
snippet.description:
ABC News' Elwyn Lopez reports on the return to dating as more Americans get vaccinated, with some turning from monogamy towards polyamory.

ABC News Live Prime, Weekdays at 7EST & 9EST
